      "description": "Context: A demo dashboard should be operable end-to-end, not just a passive display.\n\nFocus: Provide copy/paste commands to list, add, reload, and remove demo targets consistently.\n\nImplementation: Backed by the Makefile.demo helper targets to ensure the same workflow is used every time and changes are validated via Prometheus reload metrics.\n\nSecurity: Commands avoid handling secrets; target changes are configuration-only and verified through exported metrics rather than privileged access.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
